hadiths[21]{hadithnumber,text}:
2299,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey hukm diya tha ke un qurbani ke janwaron ki jhool aur unke chamdey ko main khairat kar dun jinhein qurbaan kya gaya tha.
2300,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh bakriyan unke hawale ki thin taake sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) mein unko taqseem kar dein. aik bakri ka bachcha baqi reh gaya. jab iska zikr unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke uski to qurbani kar ley.
2301,"maine Umayya-bin-Khalaf se ye muaahida apne aur uske darmyan likhwaayaa ke wo mere baal-bachchon ya meri jaaidaad ki jo Makka mein hai, hifazat karey aur main uski jaaidaad ki jo Madina mein hai hifazat karun. jab maine apna naam likhtey waqt Rehman ka zikr kya to usne kaha ke main Rehman ko kya jaanoon. tum apna wahi naam likhwaao jo zamana jahiliyat mein tha. chunanche maine abd Amr likhwaayaa . badr ki ladai ke mauqe par main aik pahaad ki taraf gaya taake logon se aankh bacha kar uski hifazat kar sakoon, lekin Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne dekh liya aur fauran hi Ansar ki aik majlis mein aaey. unhon-ne majlis walon se kaha ke ye dekho Umayya-bin-Khalaf ( kaafir dushmane-Islaam) idhar maujood hai. agar Umayya kaafir bach nikla to meri naakaamii hogi. chunanche unke sath Ansar ki aik jamat hamarey peechhey ho li. jab mujhey khof hua ke ab ye log hamein aa lengey to maine uske ladkey ko aagey kar diya taake uske sath (aaney wali jama'at) mashghool rahe, lekin logon ne usey qatl kar diya aur phir bhi wo hamari hi taraf badhney lagey. Umayya bahut bhari jism ka tha. aakhir jab jama'ate-ansaar ne hamein aa liya to maine us se kaha ke zameen par let jaa. jab wo zameen par let gaya to maine apna jism uske uper daal diya. taake logon ko rok sakoon, lekin logon ne mere jism ke nichey se uske jism par talwaar ki chotein lagaaein aur usey qatl karke hi chhodaa. aik sahabi ne apni talwaar se mere paon ko bhi zakhmi kar diya tha. Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) iska nishan apne qadam ke uper hamein dikhaya kartey they."
2302,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs ko khaibar ka tehseel daar banaya. wo umda qism ki khajoor laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse malum farmaya ke kya khaibar ki tamam khajoorein usi qism ki hain. unhon-ne kaha ke ham is tarah ki aik saa khajoor (is se ghatiyaa qism ki) 2 saa khajoor ke badal main aur 2 saa , teen saa ke badley mein khareedtey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hidayat farmai ke aisa na kar, albatta ghatiyaa khajooron ko paisoon ke badley bech kar unse achi qism ki khajoor khareed saktey ho. aur tauley janey ki chizon mein bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahi hukm farmaya,"
2303,"rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs ko khaibar ka tehseel daar banaya. wo umda qism ki khajoor laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse malum farmaya ke kya khaibar ki tamam khajoorein usi qism ki hain. unhon-ne kaha ke ham is tarah ki aik saa khajoor (is se ghatiyaa qism ki) 2 saa khajoor ke badal main aur 2 saa , teen saa ke badley mein khareedtey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hidayat farmai ke aisa na kar, albatta ghatiyaa khajooron ko paisoon ke badley bech kar unse achi qism ki khajoor khareed saktey ho. aur tauley janey ki chizon mein bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahi hukm farmaayaa,"
2304,"unke paas bakriyon ka aik rewad tha. jo Sala pahaadii par charney jata tha ( unhon-ne bayan kya ke) hamari aik baandi ne hamarey hi rewad ki aik bakri ko (jab ke wo char rahi thi) dekha ke marney ke qareeb hai. us ne aik patthar tod kar us se us bakri ko zabah kar diya. unhon-ne apne ghar walon se kaha ke jab tak main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske barey mein main poochh na loon iska gosht na khaanaa. ya ( yun kaha ke) jab tak mein kisi ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein iske barey mein poochhney ke liye na bhejoon, chunanche unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske barey mein poochha, ya kisi ko (poochhney ke liye) bhejaa, aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iska gosht khaney ke liye hukm farmaya, Ubaidullah ne kaha ke mujhey ye baat ajeeb malum hui ke baandi ( aurat ( honey ke bawajud us ne zabah kar diya. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Abda ne Ubaidullah ke waaste se ki hai."
2305,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par aik shakhs ka aik khas Umr ka oont qarz tha. wo shakhs taqaza karne aaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (apne sahaba se) farmaya ke ada kar do. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne us Umr ka oont talash kya lekin nahi mila. albatta us se zyada Umr ka ( mil saka (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke yahi unhein de do. is par us shakhs ne kaha ke aap ne mujhey pooraa-pooraa haq de diya. Allah Taala aapko bhi pura badla de. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum mein sabse behtar wo log hain jo qarz wghaira ko poori tarah ada kar detey hain.
2306,"aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (apne qarz ka ( taqaza karne aaya, aur sakht guftgu karne laga. sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ghussa ho kar uski taraf badhey lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey chhod do. kyonke jiska kisi par haq ho to wo ( baat ( kehney ka bhi haq rakhta hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke iske qarz waley janwar ki Umr ka aik janwar usey de do. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ya Rasulullah ! us se zyada Umr ka janwar to maujood hai. (lekin us Umr ka nahi (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey wahi de do. kyonke sabse achchha aadmi wo hai jo dusron ka haq poori tarah ada kar de."
2307,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein (jange-Hunain ke baad) jab qabila Hawazin ka wafad musalman ho kar hazir hua to unhon-ne darkhaast ki ke unke maal w daulat aur unke qaidi unhein wapas kar diye jaaein. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sabse zyada sachchii baat mujhey sabse zyada pyari hai. tumhen apne 2 mataalbon mein se sirf kisi aik ko ikhtiyar karna hoga, ya qaidi wapas ley lo, ya maal ley lo, main is par ghaur karne ki wafad ko mohlat bhi deta hun. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Taaif se waapsii ke baad unka (Ja'araana mein) taqriban das raat tak intizar kya. phir jab qabila Hawazin ke wakeelon par ye baat waazeh ho gaee ke aap unke mutaalbe ka sirf aik hi hissey taslim kar saktey hain to unhon-ne kaha ke ham sirf apne un logon ko wapas lena chahtey hain jo aap ki qaid mein hain. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne musalmanon ko khitab farmaya, pahley Allah Taala ki uski shaan ke mutabiq hamd w sana bayan ki, phir farmaya, ammaa ba'd! ye tumharey bhai tauba karke musalman ho kar tumharey paas aaey hain. isliye maine munasib jana ke unke qaidiyon ko wapas kar dun. ab jo shakhs apni khushi se aisa karna chahey to usey kar guzrey aur jo shakhs ye chahta ho ke iska hissey baqi rahe aur ham iske us hisse ko) qeemat ki shakl mein) us waqt wapas kar dein jab Allah Taala (aaj ke baad) sabse pahlaa maale-ghanimat kahin se dila de to usey bhi kar guzarna chahiye ye sun kar sab log bol padey ke ham b-khushi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khaatir unke qaidiyon ko chhodney ke liye taiyaar hain. lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is tarah ham uski tameez nahi kar saktey ke tum mein se kis ne ijazat di hai aur kis ne nahi di hai. isliye tum sab (apne apney deron mein) wapas jao aur wahan se tumharey wakeel tumhara faisla hamarey paas laaein. chunanche sab log wapas chaley gaey aur unke sardaaron ne (jo unke numaaindey they) is sura haal par baat ki phir wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aapko bataya ke sab ne b-khushi dil se ijazat de di hai."
2308,"nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein (jange-Hunain ke baad) jab qabila Hawazin ka wafad musalman ho kar hazir hua to unhon-ne darkhaast ki ke unke maal w daulat aur unke qaidi unhein wapas kar diye jaaein. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sabse zyada sachchii baat mujhey sabse zyada pyari hai. tumhen apne 2 mataalbon mein se sirf kisi aik ko ikhtiyar karna hoga, ya qaidi wapas ley lo, ya maal ley lo, main is par ghaur karne ki wafad ko mohlat bhi deta hun. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Taaif se waapsii ke baad unka (Ja'araana mein) taqriban das raat tak intizar kya. phir jab qabila Hawazin ke wakeelon par ye baat waazeh ho gaee ke aap unke mutaalbe ka sirf aik hi hissey taslim kar saktey hain to unhon-ne kaha ke ham sirf apne un logon ko wapas lena chahtey hain jo aap ki qaid mein hain. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne musalmanon ko khitab farmaya, pahley Allah Taala ki uski shaan ke mutabiq hamd w sana bayan ki, phir farmaya, ammaa ba'd! ye tumharey bhai tauba karke musalman ho kar tumharey paas aaey hain. isliye maine munasib jana ke unke qaidiyon ko wapas kar dun. ab jo shakhs apni khushi se aisa karna chahey to usey kar guzrey aur jo shakhs ye chahta ho ke iska hissey baqi rahe aur ham iske us hisse ko) qeemat ki shakl mein) us waqt wapas kar dein jab Allah Taala (aaj ke baad) sabse pahlaa maale-ghanimat kahin se dila de to usey bhi kar guzarna chahiye ye sun kar sab log bol padey ke ham b-khushi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khaatir unke qaidiyon ko chhodney ke liye taiyaar hain. lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is tarah ham uski tameez nahi kar saktey ke tum mein se kis ne ijazat di hai aur kis ne nahi di hai. isliye tum sab (apne apney deron mein) wapas jao aur wahan se tumharey wakeel tumhara faisla hamarey paas laaein. chunanche sab log wapas chaley gaey aur unke sardaaron ne (jo unke numaaindey they) is sura haal par baat ki phir wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aapko bataya ke sab ne b-khushi dil se ijazat de di hai."
2309,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar mein tha aur main aik sust oont par Sawar tha aur wo sabse aakhir mein rehta tha. ittifaq se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka guzar meri taraf se hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye kon sahib hain? maine arz kya Jabir-bin-Abdullah , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya baat hui (ke itney peechhey reh gaey ho) main bola ke aik bahut hi zyada sust raftaar oont par Sawar hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, tumharey paas koi chhadi bhi hai? maine kaha ke ji haan hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo mujhey de-dey. maine aap ki khidmat mein wo pesh kar di. aap ne us chhadi se oont ko jo maara aur daantaa to uske baad wo sabse aagey rehney laga. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya ke ye oont mujhey farokht kar de. maine arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! ye to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka hi hai, lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey mujhey bech de. ye bhi farmaya ke char Dinar mein usey main khareedtaa hon waisey tum Madina tak usi par Sawar ho kar chal saktey ho. phir jab Madina ke qareeb ham pahunchey to main (doosri taraf) janey laga. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kahan ja rahe ho? maine arz kya ke maine aik bewa aurat se shadi kar li hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kisi kunwaarii se kyon na ki ke tum bhi uske sath kheltey aur wo bhi tumharey sath kheltii . maine arz kya ke walid shahadat pa chukey hain. aur ghar mein kai bahnein hain. isliye maine sochaa ke kisi aisi khatun se shadi karun jo bewa aur tajriba kaar ho. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir to theek hai, phir Madina pahunchne ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Bilaal! unki qeemat ada kar do aur kuchh badha kar de do. chunanche unhon-ne char Dinar bhi diye aur faaltu aik qirat bhi diya. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye inaam main apne se kabhi juda nahi karta, chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka wo qirat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) hamesha apni thaili mein mehfooz rakha kartey they."
2310,aik aurat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! maine khud ko aapko bakhsh diya. is par aik sahabi ne kaha ke aap mera unse nikah kar dijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine tumhara nikah unse us mehar ke sath kya jo tumhen Quran yad hai.
2311,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey Ramazan ki zakat ki hifazat par muqarrar farmaya, (raat mein) aik shakhs achcha mere paas aaya aur ghalle mein se lap bhar-bhar kar uthaney laga maine usey pakad liya aur kaha ke qism Allah ki! main tujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley chaloonga. is par usne kaha ke Allah ki qasam! main bahut mohtaaj hun. mere baal bachchey hain aur main sakht zarurat mand hun. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha (iske izhaare-ma'zirat par) maine usey chhod diya. subah hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se poochha, aey abu-Huraira! pichhli raat tumharey qaidi ne kaha kya tha? maine kaha ya Rasulullah! us ne sakht zarurat aur baal bachchon ka ronaa royaa, isliye mujhey is par raham aa gaya aur maine usey chhod diya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo tum se jhoot bol kar gaya hai. abhi wo phir aayega. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us farmaney ki wjah se mujh ko yaqin tha ke wo phir zaroor aayega. isliye main uski taak mein laga raha aur jab wo dusri raat aa ke phir ghalla uthaney laga to maine usey phir pakda aur kaha ke tujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir karunga, lekin ab bhi uski wahi iltijaa thi ke mujhey chhod de, main mohtaaj hun. baal-bachchon ka bojh mere sar par hai. ab main kabhi na aaoonga. mujhey raham aa gaya aur maine usey phir chhod diya. subah hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aey abu-Huraira! tumharey qaidi ne kya kahaa? maine kaha ya Rasulullah! us ne phir usi sakht zarurat aur baal bachchon ka ronaa royaa. jis par mujhey raham aa gaya. isliye maine usey chhod diya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us martaba bhi yahi farmaya ke wo tum se jhoot bol kar gaya hai aur wo phir aayega. teesri martaba main phir iske intizar mein tha ke usne phir teesri raat aa kar ghalla uthana shuru kya, to maine usey pakad liya, aur kaha ke tujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchaanaa ab zaroori ho gaya hai. ye teesra mauqa hai. har martaba tum yaqin dilaatey rahe ke phir nahi aaogey. lekin tum baaz nahi aaey. usne kaha ke us martaba mujhey chhod de to main tumhen aisey chand kalimaat sikhaa doonga jis se Allah Taala tumhen fayda pahunchaaeyga. maine puchha wo kalimaat kya hain? us ne kaha, jab tum apne bistar par letney lago to aayatal-kursii (الله لا إله إلا هو الحي القيوم) poorii padh liya karo. aik nigraan farishta Allah Taala ki taraf se barabar tumhari hifazat karta rahega aur subah tak shaitan tumharey paas bhi nahi aa sakega. us martaba bhi phir maine usey chhod diya. subah hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya, pichhli raat tumharey qaidi ne tum se kya mamla kya? maine arz kya ya Rasulullah! usne mujhey chand kalimaat sikhaaey aur yaqin dilaya ke Allah Taala mujhey us se fayda pahunchaaeyga. isliye maine usey chhod diya. aap ne malum kya ke wo kalimaat kya hain? maine arz kya ke usne bataya tha ke jab bistar par leto to aayatal-kursii padh lo, shuru' (الله لا إله إلا هو الحي القيوم)  se aakhir tak. us ne mujh se ye bhi kaha ke Allah Taala ki taraf se tum par (iske padhney se) aik nigraan farishta muqarrar rahega aur subah tak shaitan tumharey qareeb bhi nahi aa sakega. sahaba khair ko sabse aagey badh kar leney waley they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (unki ye baat sun kar) farmaya ke agarche wo jhoota tha. lekin tum se ye baat sach keh gaya hai. aey abu-Huraira! tum ko ye bhi malum hai ke teen raaton se tumhara mamla kis se tha? unhon-ne kaha nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo shaitan tha."
2312,"Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein barnii khajoor (khajoor ki aik umda qism) lekar aaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye kahan se laey ho? unhon-ne kaha hamarey paas kharaab khajoor thi, iske 2 saa iske aik saa ke badley mein de kar ham usey laey hain. taake ham ye aapko khilaaein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tauba tauba ye to sood hai bilkul sood. aisa na kya kar albatta (achchhii khajoor) kharidney ka irada ho to (kharaab) khajoor bech kar (iski qeemat se) umda khareedaa kar."
2313,umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne sadqe ke baab mein jo kitab likhwaaii thi usmein yun hai ke sadqey ka mutwallii usmein se kha sakta hai aur dost ko khilaa sakta hai lekin rupya na jama karey aur Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) apne walid umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke sadqey ke mutwallii they. wo Makka walon ko usmein se tohfa bhejtey they jahan aap qiyam farmaya kartey they.
2314,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ibne- Suhak Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya, aey Anees! us khatun ke yahan jaa. agar wo zina ka iqrar kar ley to usey sangsaar kar de."
2315,"nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ibne- Suhak Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya, aey Anees! us khatun ke yahan jaa. agar wo zina ka iqrar kar ley to usey sangsaar kar de."
2316,Nuaimaan ya ibne-Nuaimaan ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir kya gaya. unhon-ne sharab pi li thi. jo log us waqt ghar mein maujood they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhiin ko usey maarney ka hukm diya. unhon-ne bayan kya main bhi maarney walon se tha. ham ne jooton aur chhadiyon se unhein maara tha.
2317,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya, maine apne hathon se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qurbani ke janwaron ke haar batey they. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un janwaron ko ye haar apne hath se pehnaey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo janwar mere walid ke sath (Makka mein qurbani ke liye) bhejey. unki qurbani ki gaee. lekin (is bhejney ki wjah se) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par koi aisi cheez haram nahi hui jisey Allah Taala ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye halal kya tha."
2318,"abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) Madina mein Ansar ke sabse maaldaar logon mein se they. beerhaa (eik baagh) unka sabse zyada mahboob maal tha. jo masjide-Nabawi ke bilkul samney tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi wahan tashrif ley jatey aur iska bahut hi zyada meethaa umda pani peetey they. phir jab Quran ki aayat ( لن تنالوا البر حتى تنفقوا مما تحبون‏ ) utrii ''tum neki ko hargiz nahi hasil kar saktey jab tak na kharch karo Allah ki raah mein wo cheez jo tumhen zyada pasand ho'' to abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaey aur arz kya, ya Rasulullah! Allah Taala ne apni kitab mein farmaya hai ( لن تنالوا البر حتى تنفقوا مما تحبون‏ ) aur mujhey apne maal mein sabse zyada pasand mera yahi baagh beerhaa hai. ye Allah ki raah mein sadqa hai. uski neki aur zakheera sawab ki ummeed mein sirf Allah Taala se rakhta hun. to aap jahan munasib samjhein usey kharch farma dein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, waah waah! ye bada hi nafe wala maal hai. bahut hi mufeed hai. iske barey main tum ne jo kuchh kaha wo maine sun liya. ab main to yahi munasib samajhta hun ke usey to apne rishte daaron hi mein taqseem kar de. abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah! main aisa hi karunga. chunanche ye kunwaan unhon-ne apne rishte daaron aur chacha ki aulad mein taqseem kar diya. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Ismail ne Malik se ki hai. aur Rooh ne Malik se ( lafz (رائح‏ . Mina (ke bajaey) ( رابح‏ . Mina ( naql kya hai."
2319,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, amanat daar khazaanchii jo kharch karta hai. kuchh baar ye farmaya ke jo deta hai hukm ke mutabiq kaamil aur poori tarah jis cheez (ke diye) ka usey hukm ho aur usey detey waqt uska dil bhi khush ho, to wo bhi sadqa karne walon mein se aik hai."
